Class DeckFiller<T>

java.lang.Object
juno.model.deck.AbstractDiscardedPileUser<T>
juno.model.deck.DeckFiller<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the cards.
All Implemented Interfaces:
InterfaceDeckFiller<T>, Observable
public class DeckFiller<T> extends AbstractDiscardedPileUser<T> implements InterfaceDeckFiller<T>, Observable
This class defines a card deck filler of type 'InterfaceCard'. The fill method fills the specified deck with cards contained within the supplier deck according to the rules of 'Uno'.
